246
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:45,640
You left them in the well to die slowly?

247
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:47,610
I wanted to give them a quick death,

248
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:48,890
but...

249
00:12:48,890 --> 00:12:50,490
