269
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,280
but actually serves the powerful

270
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:45,980
by doing their dirty work,

271
00:13:46,020 --> 00:13:47,400
gaining connections

272
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:49,760
