273
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,440
Could the Yang mother and daughter

274
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,210
have been kidnapped by the pawnshop too?

275
00:13:55,210 --> 00:13:57,610
They only took the young one at first,

276
00:13:58,330 --> 00:14:02,380
but Concubine Yang
loved her daughter so much

277
00:14:02,490 --> 00:14:04,460
